In our client engagements at Redevise, we regularly design and deploy these solutions. For example, when partnering with a fast-growing team in 2024, we measured knowledge scores. The initial score was 62 percent. The team was asking 38 percent of the time. We invested in documentation. Contextual SOP delivery. Better tooling. After three months, the score was 84 percent. The team was handling more volume with the same headcount.

